title: ‘The Challenge: All Stars’ Season 3, Episode 4 With Jemmye | Death, Taxes, and Bananas
description:
Johnny is joined this week by 'Challenge' legend and two-time 'All Star' Jemmye Carroll to go through Episode 4 of ‘All Stars’ Season 3, and to tell some of their favorite stories from their time together on ‘The Challenge.’
Host: Johnny Bananas
Guest: Jemmye Carroll
Producer: Sasha Ashall
